+ Understand the\nStructured Streaming Model
++ Unbounded Table Concept
+++_ Data stream = continuously growing table
+++_ Same DataFrame API as batch
+++_ spark.readStream instead of spark.read
++ Core Pattern
+++_ 1. Configure source (readStream)
+++_ 2. Apply transformations
+++_ 3. Write to sink (writeStream + checkpoint)
-- Checkpoints
---_ Track processed records
---_ Enable fault-tolerant restart
---_ Resume from last checkpoint on failure
-- Use Cases
---_ IoT sensor readings
---_ Clickstream data
---_ Financial transactions
@endmindmap
